# Optional. For `npm run dev`, omit this: the app calls `/api/v1` on the same host as the page
# and Vite proxies `/api` → FastAPI (works from phone: `http://<your-pc-ip>:5173`).
# Set when the API runs on another host (e.g. production):
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com/api/v1
#
# If your backend is not on 127.0.0.1:8000 locally, override the proxy target (vite.config):
# VITE_DEV_BACKEND_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:9000
